<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RADDsp<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>standalone<sp/>DSP<sp/>module<sp/>for<sp/>audio,<sp/>SDR/IQ,<sp/>plotting,<sp/>and<sp/>analysis</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">tools.<sp/>It<sp/>intentionally<sp/>has<sp/>no<sp/>dependency<sp/>on<sp/>RADMedia<sp/>so<sp/>it<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>reused<sp/>across</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">different<sp/>data<sp/>sources.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Current<sp/>primitives<sp/>include<sp/>gain,<sp/>mixing,<sp/>peak/RMS,<sp/>normalization,<sp/>sine/noise</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">generation,<sp/>interleave/deinterleave,<sp/>linear<sp/>resampling,<sp/>windows,<sp/>FIR<sp/>filtering,</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">one-pole<sp/>low-pass<sp/>filtering,<sp/>and<sp/>complex/IQ<sp/>magnitude,<sp/>phase,<sp/>gain,<sp/>and</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">frequency<sp/>shifting.</highlight></codeline>
